\ load-library ( name -- ) — load lib/<name>[.h2o] from beside the water
\ binary, symlinks resolved, independent of the process cwd.

\ === a bare name gains .h2o; the plot library defines figure ===
"plot" load-library
' figure drop "loaded" . cr                  \ loaded

\ === an explicit extension is used as given ===
"plot.h2o" load-library
"again" . cr                                 \ again

\ === a missing library errors (message elided: it carries a machine path) ===
[: "no-such-library" load-library :] catch nip . cr   \ 1
